data.description: Welcome to this near brand new, stunning 3 bed, 3 bath home in Carriage Trails! The spacious front family room with recessed lighting leads into the kitchen which includes beautiful vinyl flooring, recessed lighting, kitchen island, sleek cabinetry, and granite countertops. The kitchen also has walkout access to the backyard and is open to the living room, perfect for entertaining! Upstairs is a spacious loft that can be used as a flex space and includes storage. The primary bedroom is large and bright with a modern ensuite full bath, dual vanity, separate tub and shower and large walk-in closet! The additional bedrooms are bright and spacious as well with carpet flooring and recessed lighting. With a 2 car garage, large backyard, and gorgeous modern features throughout, make sure to schedule your showing now!    Buyer to verify tax information and all details. New construction not all information has updated with the county yet.
